1402.name: OA 64
1402.Applications: Rebuilding wornout parts or protecting new machine parts to increase life that suffer from grinding wear combined with increased temperatures.
1402.Suitable_For: For fire gratings, sintering plants, augers and blast furnace bells ,gravel washing equipment, sugar mill hammer and knives, clinker crushers, coal mill rollers, screw conveyors, sintering lines, mixer blades etc.
